谢谢大家
Thank you.

92
00:07:05,500 --> 00:07:06,651
你得阻止这家伙
You've got to stop him doing that.

93
00:07:06,652 --> 00:07:08,590
弄的我们像白痴一样
He's making us look like idiots.

94
00:07:08,620 --> 00:07:11,580
