省省吧
Don't bother.

708
00:38:23,620 --> 00:38:25,855
这么快就对他死心塌地了
You're very loyal VERY quickly.

709
00:38:25,890 --> 00:38:28,770
不 不是 我只是不感兴趣
No, I'm not, I'm just not interested.

710
00:38:33,040 --> 00:38:36,060
"不信任人" 医生写的
"Trust issues"... it says here.

