What's that?

712
00:38:40,650 --> 00:38:42,450
你居然不信任其他人
Could it be that you've decided to

713
00:38:42,485 --> 00:38:44,250
却信任夏洛克·福尔摩斯?
trust Sherlock Holmes of all people?

714
00:38:44,285 --> 00:38:45,265
谁说我信任他了?
Who says I trust him?

715
00:38:45,300 --> 00:38:47,280
